*bluez-utils-3.10-r1 (12 May 2007)

  12 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  +files/bluez-utils-3.10-init.d, +bluez-utils-3.10-r1.ebuild:
  Change init script to have use dbus instead of after dbus as hcid doesn't
  work without dbus running. Fixes bug #178158.

  11 May 2007; Gustavo Zacarias <gustavoz@gentoo.org>
  bluez-utils-3.10.ebuild:
  Keyworded ~sparc wrt #178071

  11 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  bluez-utils-3.10.ebuild:
  Add net-wireless/kdebluetooth as a pin key helper provider to pkg_postinst.

